sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Controller Reconciler
    participant SatEngine as Saturation Engine<br/>(30s loop)
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Prom as Prometheus (Thanos Querier)<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Metrics as /metrics Endpoint<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA
    participant Deploy as Deployment / LWS

    Note over Admin,Deploy: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Loop

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create VariantAutoscaling CR
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event (VA created)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read ConfigMaps<br/>(saturation, queueing model)

    loop Every 30 seconds
        SatEngine->>K8sAPI: List VariantAutoscaling CRs<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>SatEngine: Active VA list
        SatEngine->>Prom: PromQL: vllm:kv_cache_usage_perc,<br/>num_requests_waiting, token rates<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Prom-->>SatEngine: Metrics response

        Note over SatEngine: Run V1/V2/QM analyzers<br/>Apply GPU limiter if enabled

        SatEngine->>Cache: Store scaling decision<br/>(desired replicas per VA)
        Cache-->>Controller: DecisionTrigger channel
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch VA status<br/>(desired replicas, conditions)<br/>Auth: SA Token
    end

    Prom->>Metrics: Scrape wva_desired_replicas,<br/>wva_current_replicas,<br/>wva_desired_ratio<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    HPA->>Metrics: Read custom metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    HPA->>K8sAPI: Scale Deployment<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Deploy: Update replicas

    Note over Admin,Deploy: Flow 2: Scale-From-Zero Cold Start

    participant SFZEngine as Scale-From-Zero Engine<br/>(100ms loop)
    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>HTTP

    loop Every 100ms
        SFZEngine->>K8sAPI: List inactive VAs (replicas=0)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>SFZEngine: Inactive VA list
        SFZEngine->>EPP: GET flow_control_queue_size<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (EPP token)
        EPP-->>SFZEngine: Queue size > 0
        SFZEngine->>K8sAPI: PATCH /scale subresource<br/>(set replicas=1)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>Deploy: Scale to 1 replica
        SFZEngine->>Cache: Store decision (replicas=1)
    end
